originalSql:
SELECT 
    p.Id AS PostID,
    p.Title,
    u.DisplayName AS Owner,
    p.CreationDate,
    p.ViewCount,
    p.Score,
    (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Comments c WHERE c.PostId = p.Id) AS CommentCount
FROM 
    Posts p
JOIN 
    Users u ON p.OwnerUserId = u.Id
WHERE 
    p.PostTypeId = 1 
ORDER BY 
    p.CreationDate DESC
LIMIT 10
